00:04:15.749 --> 00:04:18.002
So, we are constraining
ourselves to the points

00:04:18.002 --> 00:04:20.300
that sit on this line,
but we want to be part

00:04:20.300 --> 00:04:22.088
of the solution set.

00:04:22.088 --> 00:04:25.420
So we want to be on this line

00:04:25.420 --> 00:04:27.312
that constrains us to x equals four,

00:04:27.312 --> 00:04:30.087
but we want to be in the
overlap of the solution sets

00:04:30.087 --> 00:04:33.041
of the two inequalities in
order to satisfy the system.

00:04:33.041 --> 00:04:34.433
So, let's see.

00:04:34.433 --> 00:04:38.598
We want to be in this
area right over here,

00:04:38.598 --> 00:04:41.279
that's the overlap of the solutions sets

00:04:41.279 --> 00:04:43.525
of the two inequalities.

00:04:43.525 --> 00:04:46.930
And so, if we constrain
ourselves to x equaling four,

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:51.787
y has to be greater than
because we're not including

00:04:51.787 --> 00:04:54.259
