00:05:12.278 --> 00:05:14.948
So anything that's on the
blue line is still going

00:05:14.948 --> 00:05:18.233
to be on the solution set
of the blue inequality.

00:05:18.233 --> 00:05:20.497
And this point that I'm
showing right here is clearly

00:05:20.497 --> 00:05:23.736
